  <brief_title>StaphVAX Immunogenicity and Safety in Orthopaedic Joint Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Double-Blinded Study to Evaluate Safety and Immunogenicity of StaphVAX®, a Bivalent Staphylococcus Aureus Glycoconjugate Vaccine in Adult Patients Receiving an Orthopedic Prosthetic Implant</official_title>
